nodes.text: Mission to recover Atom Edge's supplies

After the Rebel Alliance freighter Atom Edge split in half in Tatooine's orbit, the Rebel Alliance, Galactic Empire, and mercenaries raced to the crash sites. After the rebels drove off the Empire and recovered the supplies, the conflict would begin the operations on Tatooine, a campaign by the Rebel Alliance to expel the Empire from Tatooine.
